## Summary

At the top of the page, show a summary for the selected period:

* Number of shifts
* Number of workdays
* Approved work hours
* Number of shifts as ראש צוות
* Number of shifts with pending attendance corrections
* Number of missing or overdue forms

Do not show an estimated payment total in this section until the approximate-payment feature is finalized.

Example:

```text
אוגוסט 2026

12 עבודות
58 שעות ו-30 דקות מאושרות
3 עבודות כראש צוות
תיקון נוכחות אחד מחכה לאישור
```

---

## Calendar Integration

Past shifts should remain visible in the worker calendar.

Past calendar cards should show:

* Completed status
* Clock-in and clock-out times
* Attendance issue indicator
* Missing-form indicator

Clicking a past calendar shift should open the same shift-detail view used by the history page.

---

## Monthly Report Integration

Every job line in a monthly report should link to its corresponding shift-history entry.

The values in the monthly report should be based on the approved attendance shown in the shift history.

When there is a difference between shift history and a published report, show:

```text
השעות בדוח אינן תואמות לשעות המאושרות בעבודה
```

The worker should be able to create a correction comment directly from that shift.

---

## Data Visibility Rules

Workers may see:

* Their own recorded attendance
* Their own approved attendance
* Their own correction requests
* Their own submitted forms
* Customer and shift information
* Names of workers who were assigned to the shift

Workers may not see:

* Attendance times of other workers
* Other workers' pay
* Internal owner comments
* Owner-only worker-log entries
* Location history or raw location samples
* Internal reliability indicators

---

## Acceptance Criteria

* Workers can view all past shifts they attended.
* Past shifts are ordered from newest to oldest.
* Each shift shows scheduled, recorded, and approved attendance when applicable.
* Approved payable duration is clearly displayed.
* Pending attendance corrections are visibly marked.
* Workers can open a detailed shift view.
* Shift history links to the relevant monthly report.
* Monthly report lines link back to the shift.
* Past shifts remain visible in the calendar.
* Workers cannot see other workers' attendance records.
* Workers cannot see the owner-only worker log.
* Workers can filter history by month, year, type, customer, role, and status.
